Class MockerVisitor

java.lang.Object
org.objectweb.asm.ClassVisitor
fr.umlv.retro.mocker.MockerVisitor
All Implemented Interfaces:
FeatureVisitor
public class MockerVisitor
extends org.objectweb.asm.ClassVisitor
implements FeatureVisitor
Mock unsupported JDK apis if not supported in target version. Example. java.util.function.* is not supported for a target JDK < 8
